long_description: The Nite Ize Key Rack is compact, simple, versatile, colorful and cool! It organizes and color-codes 6 keys in a simple, quick-release design. High quality, stainless-steel carabiner clip features a secure gate closure-attach it to an existing key ring, belt loop, purse strap or zipper pull with ease. 6 differently colored plastic S-Biners color-code keys and detach individually for convenience.
